  "text": "The numerical model bundled with the MD code was based on the FEM technique, which simulated light propagation through an EBT3 film with different light-absorption coefficients. The FEM model simulated the realistic experimental set-up in which the EBT3 film was scanned. The classical steady-state Helmholtz equation was used to model the re-emittance (i.e., reflection) from and transmittance through the EBT3 film [CITATION_1] : ",
